Madeleine Ozeray https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Madeleine_Ozeray 0 Madeleine Ozeray (13 September 1908 in Bouillon – 28 March 1989 ), was a French stage and film actress. She appeared in many films between 1932 and 1980. She is the godmother of theater actor, dancer and singer Frédéric Norbert.
